msgstr "目录"

#: ../../index.rst:3
msgid "JinWu Documentation"
msgstr "金乌文档"

#: ../../index.rst:5
msgid ""
"**Joint Inference for high-energy transient light-curve & spectral "
"analysis with Unifying physical modeling.**"
msgstr ""
"**高能暂现源光变曲线与能谱的联合分析，基于统一物理建模。**"

#: ../../index.rst:8
msgid ""
"JinWu (金乌) is a comprehensive Python toolkit for X-ray and gamma-ray "
"astrophysics, bringing together spectral and temporal analysis with "
"unified physical modeling.  Named after the mythical three-legged golden "
"crow dwelling in the sun — a fitting symbol for a package that shines "
"light on the most energetic transients in the Universe."
msgstr ""
"金乌 (JinWu) 是一个面向 X 射线和伽马射线天体物理的综合性 Python "
"工具包，将能谱分析和时变分析统一于物理建模框架之下。其名取自神话中"
"居于太阳的三足金乌——恰如其分地象征着一个照亮宇宙中最高能暂现源的"
"软件包。"

#: ../../index.rst:30
msgid "Key Features"
msgstr "主要特性"

#: ../../index.rst:32
msgid ""
"**OGIP FITS I/O** — Read and write ARF, RMF, PHA, lightcurve, and event "
"files"
msgstr ""
"**OGIP FITS 输入/输出** — 读写 ARF、RMF、PHA、光变曲线和事件文件"

#: ../../index.rst:33
msgid ""
"**Lightcurve & Spectral Analysis** — Background modeling, trigger "
"evaluation, XSPEC-inspired components"
msgstr ""
"**光变曲线与能谱分析** — 背景建模、触发评估、XSPEC 风格的组件"

#: ../../index.rst:34
msgid ""
"**Multi-mission Support** — Einstein Probe (EP), Fermi/GBM, Swift/BAT, "
"and more"
msgstr ""
"**多任务支持** — 爱因斯坦探针 (EP)、Fermi/GBM、Swift/BAT 等"

#: ../../index.rst:35
msgid ""
"**Unified Physical Modeling** — Consistent framework across bands and "
"messengers"
msgstr ""
"**统一物理建模** — 跨波段、跨信使的一致性框架"

#: ../../index.rst:36
msgid ""
"**Pure-Python ftools** — HEASOFT-compatible tools written entirely in "
"Python"
msgstr ""
"**纯 Python ftools** — 完全以 Python 编写的 HEASOFT 兼容工具"

#: ../../index.rst:37
msgid ""
"**Upper Limit Computation** — Bayesian & frequentist upper limits for "
"faint transients"
msgstr ""
"**上限计算** — 针对暗弱暂现源的贝叶斯与频率学派上限"

#: ../../index.rst:40
msgid "Installation"
msgstr "安装"

#: ../../index.rst:42
msgid ""
"JinWu's spectral fitting and XSPEC integration depend on "
"**HEASoft/PyXspec** and XSPEC model data.  We recommend installing these "
"via the HEASARC conda channel, though any working HEASoft installation is"
" fine."
msgstr ""
"金乌的能谱拟合和 XSPEC 集成依赖于 **HEASoft/PyXspec** 和 XSPEC "
"模型数据。我们推荐通过 HEASARC conda 频道安装，不过任何可用的 "
"HEASoft 安装均可。"

#: ../../index.rst:57
msgid ""
"If you already have HEASoft installed outside conda (e.g. from source), "
"JinWu can still use it — call "
":class:`jinwu.core.heasoft.HeasoftEnvManager` to initialize the "
"environment:"
msgstr ""
"如果您已经通过 conda 以外的方式（如源码编译）安装了 HEASoft，金乌"
"仍然可以使用它——调用 :class:`jinwu.core.heasoft.HeasoftEnvManager` "
"来初始化环境："

#: ../../index.rst:67
msgid "For development:"
msgstr "开发环境："

#: ../../index.rst:78
msgid ""
"The ``HeasoftEnvManager`` also works in Jupyter notebooks — use "
":meth:`HeasoftEnvManager.init_heasoft_in_notebook`."
msgstr ""
"``HeasoftEnvManager`` 也可在 Jupyter notebook 中使用——调用 "
":meth:`HeasoftEnvManager.init_heasoft_in_notebook`。"

